FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1407 on Page 4, Line 10, by inserting, after the period and before
the word “Expenditures”, the following language and amending the title to conform:
“The Director of the Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall provide the Commission
an itemized accounting of all monies deposited into the fund and all expenditures made from the
fund.”
